item.title: CVE-2017-3761|2024-09-17T03:29:06.189Z -- lenovo%20group%20ltd. -- service%20framework%20application
item.description: The Lenovo Service Framework Android application executes some system commands without proper sanitization of external input. In certain cases, this could lead to command injection which, in turn, could lead to remote code execution.
